{"tid":2017382,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"滕麗名否認違禁聚令","createTime":"2020-05-15T05:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T06:10:47.000Z","uid":3747,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c8253fd0388c3a521cafc42f338ab36bb84313","tid":2017382,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"藝人滕麗名與陳浚霆昨日到電台宣傳處境劇《愛．回家之開心速遞》，重返劇集的陳浚霆自爆被媽媽顧紀筠叮囑不要對呂慧儀太Mean︰「我話係角色需要，同埋希望可以同阿滕多啲對手戲，但暫時未寫到。」<br />\n<br />\n提到阿滕日前跟林淑敏、袁文傑等共9人行山，似乎違反8人的禁聚令，她解釋：「其實我哋冇可能9個人一齊行，每個人行山速度都唔同，都係2至4個分開行。我係高手之中嘅腳短，袁文傑就係高手之中嘅腳長，慶幸佢做先頭部隊，因為沿途好多蜘蛛網，佢高得滯，成口都係蜘蛛﹗」"},{"pid":"c4ce1f311423d3f296375ef7ab20fcfeb6885455","tid":2017382,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"謄麗明對腳都短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6f9d3fe183bb20d2127110a59d686a848f7f0a","tid":2017382,"uid":93060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁組隊去踢波都無問題啦 無理由22條友痴埋一齊踢"},{"pid":"9676d372dd8514a9792e86180f6bf6192e0a0a65","tid":2017382,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6f9d3fe183bb20d2127110a59d686a848f7f0a","tid":2017382,"uid":93060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁組隊去踢波都無問題啦 無理由22條友痴埋一齊踢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"咁你就錯喇 角球呢<img src=\"/assets/fa